%help
fmri_conncalc_JSins

FMRI functional connectivity processing (specific to JS insula study).

TO BUILD
We expect to build from fmri_conncalc directory:
  sudo singularity build fmri_conncalc_isins.simg Singularity.jsins.v1.0.0 

TO RUN
  singularity run --cleanenv -B <INDIR>:/INPUTS,<OUTDIR>:/OUTPUTS fmri_conncalc_jsins.simg

INPUTS
In the bound INPUTS directory:

coreg_mat.txt,FILE,INIT_COREG_MAT of MAGM_Coreg_Normalize_v2
y_deffwd.nii.gz,FILE,FWD_DEF of MAGM_Coreg_Normalize_v2
